{"tid":267962,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)藥到病除 近蛛者殺 house of dead","createTime":"2017-06-02T16:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T19:31:50.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf09c0da9fc5b8a003af333757723b7c39595b2","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=SLpKtnFz8bAHIqZcHhNgMDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=56fd4fa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=SLpKtnFz8bAHIqZcHhNgMDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=21d8e3cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=SLpKtnFz8bAHIqZcHhNgMDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4ce3f856\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://tube.hk//images/titles_cache/750x1083_movie14214postersa_cure_for_wellness-hk_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftube.hk%2F%2Fimages%2Ftitles_cache%2F750x1083_movie14214postersa_cure_for_wellness-hk_2.jpg&h=360978e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/c0/Eightleggedfreaks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fc%2Fc0%2FEightleggedfreaks.jpg&h=07da0709&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.thewebsiteofthedead.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scan-28.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewebsiteofthedead.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F05%2FScan-28.jpeg&h=41033ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.我們內裡都有一種病，歡迎接受非一般的「治命」療程。小員工（戴恩迪翰）被派往瑞士阿爾卑斯山區的一間歐式溫泉療養院，奉命接回他的老闆，才踏進中心沒多久，他發現老闆人間蒸發外，更是鬼影幢幢充滿許多暗黑秘密－－大家生了什麼病？為何所有療養院病人有入無出？在這貌似擁有全世界最美風景的角落，到底藏著什麼驚人故事？<br />\n<br />\n2.當含有劇毒的化學廢料碰上了毒性強烈的蜘蛛，會產生出什麼樣的怪物？一個偏遠靜謐的小鎮竟然在一夜之間遭逢劇變，在有毒化學廢料外洩污染的意外情況下，成千上萬的小蜘蛛在一夜之間變得碩大無朋...<br />\n只是這個小鎮裡的人並沒有意識到，一群龐然大物正對著他們悄悄而來，這些每一隻身長至少兩公尺以上的獵捕高手，將讓這個偏遠的靜謐小鎮在極短的時間內，變成人間煉獄&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.一群年輕人不顧鬧鬼的傳聞，坐著小船來到荒島準備大開派對、搖頭狂歡。但他們很快發現傳聞一點沒有虛假，那些個惡鬼僵屍開始追著他們大開殺戒。他們唯一的希望，是小島中心那座搖搖欲墜、陰森荒涼的小屋！ <br />\n<br />\n12 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9b414f809c6b5d2b955ebf220aab53798d07cf","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16a59383e5c54c6223d63d4b1c5699f64014441","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cecc6fc487f0a5e23cee7f2a642c7d7cd04b78","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832f669a77709dfa9b3706a617e906920dbd5aaf","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5368c0554ec31a850002da16dcae62db788826","tid":267962,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}